        Create a new triple with known values for the subject, relation, and object. For example, "(cats, play with, yarn)"
        Parameters:
        subject - The subject of this triple; e.g., "cats".
        relation - The relation of this triple; e.g., "play with".
        object - The object of this triple; e.g., "yarn".
        tree - The tree this extraction was created from; we create a deep copy of the tree.
